---
// src/components/inicio/Hero.astro
// Hero adaptado a datos reales de Shotokan Valladolid
---

<section id="hero" class="relative isolate overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background image -->
  <img
    src="/hero.jpg"
    alt="Alumnos entrenando en Shotokan Valladolid"
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-20 h-full w-full object-cover"
    loading="eager"
    decoding="async"
  />

  <!-- Dark gradient overlay -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/70 to-black/40"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Hero content -->
  <div class="relative z-10">
    <div class="container py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-36">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-white">
          Artes Marciales en<br />Valladolid
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base md:text-lg text-gray-300">
          En <strong>Shotokan Valladolid</strong> enseñamos disciplina, respeto y fuerza 
          a través de las artes marciales.  
          Clases de <em>Karate, Kick Boxing, Boxeo, Judo, Jiujitsu, Aikido, Taekwondo</em> y mucho más, 
          tanto para <span class="text-red-500 font-semibold">niños como adultos</span>.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <!-- Primary button (CTA principal) -->
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-red-600 transition"
          >
            Reserva tu Clase de Prueba
          </a>

          <!-- Secondary button (Ver clases) -->
          <a
            href="/classes"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition"
          >
            Ver Actividades
          </a>

          <!-- Play Video (opcional) -->
          <a
            href="#video"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition"
          >
            <span class="inline-grid place-items-center h-9 w-9 rounded-full border border-white/70">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Ver Video
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
